        <updateDate>2022-01-04T19:14:00Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Opioid Quota Openness, Transparency, and Awareness Act of 2021 or the Opioid QuOTA Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Drug Enforcement Administration to make publicly available on its website certain information regarding opioid procurement quotas.</p> <p>The term <em>opioid procurement quota</em> means the maximum quantity of opioid analgesics that a registered manufacturer may procure.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
